BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:YZPt_qIYuFRxLWrgrIiZ5
SUMMARY:Seattle Suites: An Improvised Neil Simon Comedy
DTSTAMP:20260327T033921Z
DTSTART:20260327T193000Z
DESCRIPTION:Improvised comedy in the style of Neil Simon\\\, where one hote
	l suite becomes a comedic pressure cooker for 3 hilarious improvised tales
	\\n\\n\\n\\nOne hotel suite. Countless misunderstandings. Relentless laugh
	s. \\nSeattle Suite is a laugh-driven\\\, fully improvised play inspired b
	y the style of Plaza Suite and California Suite\\\, capturing the signatur
	e humor of Neil Simon that is fast\\\, verbal\\\, and rooted in beautifull
	y human flaws. Each night\\\, a single Seattle hotel room becomes the sett
	ing for interconnected scenes inspired by your suggestions\\\, friends ove
	rshare and spiral\\\, romantic gestures go wrong\\\, awkward silences stre
	tch\\\, and small problems become big ones. The comedy comes from characte
	r and relationship\\\, building through sharp dialogue\\\, escalating tens
	ion\\\, and recognizable\\\, lived-in situations. Perfect for fans of smar
	t comedy\\\, relationship humor\\\, and classic theatrical wit.\n\nhttps:/
	/www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/seattle-suites-an-improvised-neil-sim
	on-comedy/2026-03-27/\n\nFrom Unexpected Productions
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/seattle-suites-an-improvise
	d-neil-simon-comedy/2026-03-27/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\\\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike
	 Place Market\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\, 98101\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:unexpected-productions
CATEGORIES:Unexpected Productions
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:V26dV36W_koeW0iW2ZSIM
SUMMARY:Seattle Theatresports 2026
DTSTAMP:20260327T033921Z
DTSTART:20260327T213000Z
DESCRIPTION:Seattle’s high-energy improv battle where your suggestions shap
	e every scene. Fast\\\, funny\\\, unpredictable comedy Fri. & Sat. 9:30\\n
	\\n\\n\\nWelcome to Seattle’s funnest improv comedy show\\\, a high-energy
	\\\, no-rules showdown where your ideas shape every scene. Seattle Theatre
	sports at Unexpected Productions’ Market Theater in Pike Place Market is p
	art comedy battle\\\, part game night\\\, and completely powered by the cr
	owd. Boo the judges. Cheer the Gum Wall race and laugh til it hurts! \\nEv
	ery show\\\, two teams of top Seattle improvisers go head to head\\\, perf
	orming games\\\, stories\\\, characters\\\, and scenes inspired entirely b
	y your suggestions. Judges score the rounds\\\, decide the winners\\\, and
	 shape the fun (as we boo them). No scripts. No safety nets. Just fast thi
	nking\\\, bold choices\\\, and pure creative mayhem. \\nThis isn’t your pa
	rents’ improv show\\\, unless your parents were super cool.\n\nhttps://www
	.unexpectedproductions.org/event/seattle-theatresports-2026-test/2026-03-2
	7/\n\nFrom Unexpected Productions
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/seattle-theatresports-2026-
	test/2026-03-27/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\\\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike
	 Place Market\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\, 98101\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:unexpected-productions
CATEGORIES:Unexpected Productions
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
